<subSubSection id="47A22ED7FF9FFFE5FF24FC2D4DEFFBE5" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="0F077D5CFF9FFFE5FF24FC2D4DEFFBE5" blockId="5.[178,1086,978,1147]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">
Comment: 
<taxonomicName id="C8B806DFFF9FFFE5FEFEFC2D4E07FC76" authorityName="FAUVEL" authorityYear="1895" box="[360,602,978,1000]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Stilicoderus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fenestratus">
<emphasis id="3DCCA14EFF9FFFE5FEFEFC2D4E07FC76" box="[360,602,978,1000]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">Stilicoderus fenestratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
had been recorded from 
<collectingCountry id="77AF3DCCFF9FFFE5FCF9FC2D4FF3FC76" box="[879,942,978,1000]" name="Nepal" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">Nepal</collectingCountry>
, North 
<collectingCountry id="77AF3DCCFF9FFFE5FB95FC2D4867FC76" box="[1027,1082,978,1000]" name="India" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">India</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="77AF3DCCFF9FFFE5FF24FC0E4D4AFB98" box="[178,279,1009,1030]" name="Myanmar" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="77AF3DCCFF9FFFE5FEB2FC0F4D3DFB98" box="[292,352,1008,1030]" name="China" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">China</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion id="CD7CB3BEFF9FFFE5FEE7FC0F4D9BFB98" box="[369,454,1008,1030]" country="China" name="Yunnan" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">Yunnan</collectingRegion>
), and 
<collectingCountry id="77AF3DCCFF9FFFE5FD9EFC0F4E3FFB98" box="[520,610,1008,1030]" name="Thailand" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">Thailand</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="6B2900ADFF9FFFE5FDE4FC0F4F5DFB98" author="ASSING V" box="[626,768,1008,1030]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576" pagination="57 - 82" refId="ref7656" refString="ASSING V. (2013): New species and records of Stilicoderus and Stiliderus, primarily from the southern East Palaearctic region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde A, Neue Serie 6: 57 - 82." type="journal article" year="2013">ASSING 2013</bibRefCitation>
). The above material, the first record from 
<collectingCountry id="77AF3DCCFF9FFFE5FEA1FBF14D36FBBD" box="[311,363,1038,1059]" name="Laos" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">Laos</collectingCountry>
, is distinguished from that seen from North 
<collectingCountry id="77AF3DCCFF9FFFE5FCD5FBF24F2AFBBD" box="[835,887,1037,1059]" name="India" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576">India</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="6B2900ADFF9FFFE5FC1EFBF2484EFBBD" author="ASSING V" box="[904,1043,1037,1059]" pageId="5" pageNumber="1576" pagination="57 - 82" refId="ref7656" refString="ASSING V. (2013): New species and records of Stilicoderus and Stiliderus, primarily from the southern East Palaearctic region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde A, Neue Serie 6: 57 - 82." type="journal article" year="2013">ASSING 2013</bibRefCitation>
) by smaller body size and an aedeagus with a shorter and stouter ventral process. More material from other regions is needed to clarify if these differences are an expression of intra- or interspecific variation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
